---
title: Sichuan Garlic Pork Tacos with Crunchy Pear Salad & Crushed Peanuts
description: If you like bold flavours and Asian cuisines, you’ll love food inspired by the Sichuan province in China! We’ve dialed down the
chilli but kept the tasty garlic and umami flavours for an easy-to-eat taco that will appeal to everyone.
